                              zznyydmufs 1.01

                  Usefull support commands for MultiUser

 The usual stuff:
  @{" Introduction " Link Introduction}  What is this ?
  @{" Disclaimer   " Link Disclaimer}  If something goes wrong don't blame me
  @{" Distribution " Link Distribution}  This package is FREEWARE
